1 Currituck County Board of Elections reflects that a majority of votes cast on the question are in
2 favor of the referendum set out in subsection (d) of this section, subsections (a) through (c) of
3 this section become effective the first Monday in December 2028, and elections in 2028 and
4 thereafter shall be conducted accordingly.
5 SECTION 2.(f) Except as otherwise provided, this section is effective when it
